INSERT INTO `enquiry_fields` VALUES (1,1,'name','Si Wilkins','2011-06-01 09:06:17','2011-06-01 09:06:17'),(2,1,'comments','Testing feedback form','2011-06-01 09:06:17','2011-06-01 09:06:17'),(3,1,'email_address','si@yoomee.com','2011-06-01 09:06:17','2011-06-01 09:06:17'),(4,2,'name','Zoe-Amber ','2011-06-03 08:03:36','2011-06-03 08:03:36'),(5,2,'comments','dear reader, \r\n\r\nI joined as a member via twitter (@sphinxje), (using firefox) then it asked my email adres confirmation, that was not clickable (nothing happened), I just shut down the tab, clicked the confirmation email I did get,  opened another tab and was registered anyway aka could continue as if nothing happened. \r\n\r\nThis description probably isnt the best, but it was late yesterday and I was trying to multitask with 10 tabs and mail and so on. \r\n:)\r\n\r\nsorry guys, good luck with the site!\r\n\r\ncheers, \r\n\r\nzoe','2011-06-03 08:03:36','2011-06-03 08:03:36'),(6,2,'email_address','Zoeamber.bakker@gmail.com','2011-06-03 08:03:36','2011-06-03 08:03:36'),(7,3,'name','Zoe-Amber','2011-06-03 08:19:46','2011-06-03 08:19:46'),(8,3,'comments','Reply message after newsletter subscription is as follows:\r\n\r\nYour subscription to our list has been confirmed.\r\n\r\nFor your records, here is a copy of the information you submitted to us...\r\nCreate_date:\r\nLast Name: Bakker\r\nFirst Name: Zoe-Amber\r\nFull Name (Name + Surname):\r\nEmail Address: zoeamber.bakker@gmail.com\r\nUser_id:\r\nEnabled:\r\n\r\nIf at any time you wish to stop receiving our emails, you can unsubscribe here.\r\n\r\nI there are some fields that need to be set to hidden?\r\nCreate_date, enabled, user name?\r\n\r\nI had no idea what to fill in @ the last two.\r\n\r\ncheers!\r\nz','2011-06-03 08:19:46','2011-06-03 08:19:46'),(9,3,'email_address','Zoeamber.bakker@gmail.com','2011-06-03 08:19:46','2011-06-03 08:19:46'),(10,4,'name','Zoe-Amber','2011-06-03 08:19:48','2011-06-03 08:19:48'),(11,4,'comments','Reply message after newsletter subscription is as follows:\r\n\r\nYour subscription to our list has been confirmed.\r\n\r\nFor your records, here is a copy of the information you submitted to us...\r\nCreate_date:\r\nLast Name: Bakker\r\nFirst Name: Zoe-Amber\r\nFull Name (Name + Surname):\r\nEmail Address: zoeamber.bakker@gmail.com\r\nUser_id:\r\nEnabled:\r\n\r\nIf at any time you wish to stop receiving our emails, you can unsubscribe here.\r\n\r\nI there are some fields that need to be set to hidden?\r\nCreate_date, enabled, user name?\r\n\r\nI had no idea what to fill in @ the last two.\r\n\r\ncheers!\r\nz','2011-06-03 08:19:48','2011-06-03 08:19:48'),(12,4,'email_address','Zoeamber.bakker@gmail.com','2011-06-03 08:19:48','2011-06-03 08:19:48'),(13,5,'name','Sorana','2011-06-06 18:45:02','2011-06-06 18:45:02'),(14,5,'comments','It looks really good, congrats. There\'s one thing I suggest you check, maybe it\'s only my impression - there seems to be something wrong with the columns, sometimes they are a little bit misaligned. I\'m a bit visually impaired, so it might be my impression only. :)','2011-06-06 18:45:02','2011-06-06 18:45:02'),(15,5,'email_address','sorana.danescu@gmail.com','2011-06-06 18:45:02','2011-06-06 18:45:02'),(16,6,'name','Paul Basten','2011-06-07 12:49:39','2011-06-07 12:49:39'),(17,6,'comments','After adding a theme in the \'About the real me\' section and hitting \'Enter\' I have to click inside the textbox again to enter the next theme.\r\n\r\nThe searchbox doesn\'t include the \'About the real me\' themes. Would be nice if it did.\r\n\r\nWhen looking at your own profile, under \'your posts\' the text says \'&lt;your name=\"true\"> hasn\'t posted anything yet\'. Would be nice if it could recognize you were viewing your own profile and change \'&lt;your name=\"true\"> hasn\'t\' with \'You haven\'t\'.\r\n\r\nWould be nice if there was a central area where you could see the latest posts of other people (now I can only see the posts on their personal profile page). Could give the site a bit more life and encourage the visitors to interact with each other.\r\n\r\nWhen clicking a theme-tag you often get the message \'there are no posts with this tag\'. Either link to the profile pages of the person who added this theme to their profile to these theme tags or make the one\'s without content unclickable.\r\n\r\nThat;s it, good luck!','2011-06-07 12:49:39','2011-06-07 12:49:39'),(18,6,'email_address','paulbasten@gmail.com','2011-06-07 12:49:39','2011-06-07 12:49:39'),(19,7,'name','Paul Basten','2011-06-07 12:51:26','2011-06-07 12:51:26'),(20,7,'comments','ow, and one more thing. When I wanted to submit this form through Chrome I got an error message and couldn\'t send the form. When I copy pasted it into Safari everything went well.','2011-06-07 12:51:26','2011-06-07 12:51:26'),(21,7,'email_address','paulbasten@gmail.com','2011-06-07 12:51:26','2011-06-07 12:51:26'),(22,8,'name','Anton Hein','2011-06-08 20:20:12','2011-06-08 20:20:12'),(23,8,'comments','The location marker on the map at this URL:\r\nhttp://picnicnetwork.org/location\r\n\r\nis in the wrong spot...  It is pointing to last year\'s location.\r\n\r\nNice looking site.  \r\n\r\nYou may want to add a link to Amsterdam Tourist Information:\r\nhttp://www.dutchamsterdam.nl/\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\n\r\nAnton@dutchamsterdam.nl','2011-06-08 20:20:12','2011-06-08 20:20:12'),(24,8,'email_address','anton@dutchamsterdam.nl','2011-06-08 20:20:12','2011-06-08 20:20:12'),(25,9,'name','Kimberley Crofts','2011-06-09 00:15:19','2011-06-09 00:15:19'),(26,9,'comments','The beta works well, looks great. \r\n\r\nI have one small typographic suggestion and another about copy. \r\n\r\nI would add some padding between items on the left-hand column of the \'registration-today\' page. The thin width of this column and lack of defined space between items might make it hard for some to define separate items.\r\n\r\nOn the page \'air-france-klm-global-meetings-information\' there are some residual html tags visible in the copy.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to the festival.','2011-06-09 00:15:19','2011-06-09 00:15:19'),(27,9,'email_address','kimberley@meldstudios.com.au','2011-06-09 00:15:19','2011-06-09 00:15:19'),(28,10,'name','Bert de Boer','2011-06-09 19:46:25','2011-06-09 19:46:25'),(29,10,'comments','Hi all,\r\nLove your work and the site. It is an improvement to last year. Just \' browsing\' the mobile version, and I noticed that in portrait the site is 5px to wide. So not all words and forms are fully displayed.\r\nBut keep on the good work!\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nBert','2011-06-09 19:46:25','2011-06-09 19:46:25'),(30,10,'email_address','B.deboer@Hollandstar.com','2011-06-09 19:46:25','2011-06-09 19:46:25'),(31,11,'name','Jane Finnis','2011-06-09 20:44:12','2011-06-09 20:44:12'),(32,11,'comments','Okay, just thinking about the design of our new company website (cultural stuff in UK) and looking for inspiration. The new site have given it to me. Clean, White, simple top level nav, clear architecture. Like the grid of boxes that lead with funky images telling us all the top things we need to know. All to the point, stylish, loving (heats rule) and classy. Well done guys. Going to go and seriously try and find the money to come again (so the site has done that job well too! Fit for purpose? Yes.','2011-06-09 20:44:12','2011-06-09 20:44:12'),(33,11,'email_address','Jane@culture24.org.uk','2011-06-09 20:44:12','2011-06-09 20:44:12'),(34,12,'name','Reineke','2011-06-10 08:14:30','2011-06-10 08:14:30'),(35,12,'comments','Hi, is is true that with the new site all old registration details are gone? Info, pictures etc? I tried to login but had no success. \r\n','2011-06-10 08:14:31','2011-06-10 08:14:31'),(36,12,'email_address','reineke@postcodeloterij.nl','2011-06-10 08:14:31','2011-06-10 08:14:31'),(37,13,'name','Bart Hoekstra','2011-06-10 09:14:32','2011-06-10 09:14:32'),(38,13,'comments','I have a couple of comments that I\'d like to share:\r\n\r\n1. Main thing missing, I think, is a \'stream\' of all the things clubmembers share. I can in some way find out people are sharing through the leaderboard, but it feels kind of unnatural not being able to see that more specifically. \'Posting a new discussion\' isn\'t really clarifying. Clicking on \'discussion\' (or whatever) and then being directed to the particular thing that is being shared would be nice.\r\n2. I spot a difference between the number 1 and 2 in the leaderboards when switching views between All time and This month. All time Andy has 61 points, This month Franziska has 61 points. Seems not right to me...\r\n3. My avatar, which is not a square, is squeezed into a square when I for example visit this page: http://picnicnetwork.org/members/87/friends\r\n4. At the \'Club\' page there is an intro on the top. It has a button which says Hide this. But after you\'ve done that it says \'Show this\', which looks kind of odd. Should be something like \'Show welcome message\'.\r\n5. I would love to be able to automatically post messages to the Picnic Network through, for example, my Tumbleblog. Would be cool if all the posts I tagged with picnic11 were automatically fetched to this network...\r\n\r\nApart from this I don\'t have a lot of things to add. I really like the fact that the new site is very monochrome and minimalistic. Good work!','2011-06-10 09:14:32','2011-06-10 09:14:32'),(39,13,'email_address','barthoekstra@gmail.com','2011-06-10 09:14:32','2011-06-10 09:14:32'),(40,14,'name','Jim Bowes','2011-06-13 11:15:29','2011-06-13 11:15:29'),(41,14,'comments','Dear Beta Team,\r\n\r\nSo far so good! \r\nMy thoughts: \r\nIt would be nice if:\r\n I could welcome someone to my blanket. I invite them they come over but I am not sure how I can now reach out to them.\r\nThere was area for community posts that might help me connect with people based on issues we are interested in. \r\nPeople on my blanket chould get sent a notification when I posted. \r\nI could engage with other people?\r\n\r\nI am not a tech savvy guy so it is very possible I am just missing a button or a prompt and if so please disregard.\r\n\r\nI like having the ability to meet people before Picnic. Everyone in the Picnic Club is interesting.  However, if I can engage people I can determine which ones would be the most beneficial to meet in such a short period of time. I can also use this platform to learn from some pretty amazing people even if they do not attend or we fail to meet up. \r\n\r\nI was given a link to a book from someone I invited to sit on my blanket that has proven to be a great inspiration. So already I have gotten a great thing out of the Picnic Club.\r\nThis is a nice new addition to Picnic. It is innovative and will allow people to have a much more enjoyable and valuable Picnic experience.\r\nThanks,\r\nJim','2011-06-13 11:15:29','2011-06-13 11:15:29'),(42,14,'email_address','jim@greengraffiti.com','2011-06-13 11:15:29','2011-06-13 11:15:29'),(43,15,'name','André','2011-06-13 19:46:30','2011-06-13 19:46:30'),(44,15,'comments','I just heared about your organisation a few minutes ago.\r\n\r\nSo far i experienced:\r\n1). The last step of registration sends me to...\r\n\r\nwww.picnicnetwork.org/members/\r\n\r\n... Which gives an error page.\r\n\r\n2). I was expecting a lot of discussion topics. I have seen people posting but no post itself. Where are the ideas (graphe vine) and discussions. I think it wouls benefit everybody if it is more clear where they are (menu position) or what needs to be done to tune in.\r\n\r\n3). Adding tags to the profile is really hard with a tablet (response and layout issues), which can be the case for other (similar) fuctionality as well.\r\n\r\nFor so far: The design and look is really great.\r\n','2011-06-13 19:46:30','2011-06-13 19:46:30'),(45,15,'email_address','Craens@gmail.com','2011-06-13 19:46:30','2011-06-13 19:46:30'),(46,16,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-06-14 06:36:30','2011-06-14 06:36:30'),(47,16,'comments','This Beta is much more fun than the old site and is keeping me engaged. Still trying to work out how you can see a listing of all members / attendees .','2011-06-14 06:36:30','2011-06-14 06:36:30'),(48,16,'email_address','BarrysLounge@googlemail.com','2011-06-14 06:36:30','2011-06-14 06:36:30'),(49,17,'name','Álvaro Bootello','2011-06-16 15:29:50','2011-06-16 15:29:50'),(50,17,'comments','The website is really well developed, although I miss some more dynamism. It lacks a little color and mobility, and that\'s why it seems somewhat static; however, it works out perfectly for any mobile device, for instance.\r\nWith my opinion I\'m not saying that you\'ll have to fill everything with random \"stuff\"; the spaces are very well respected, but the bond between typography and this rather minimalist design, stays somewhat below expectations.\r\nI\'m not a web expert, but just a recent graduate in Advertising and Public Relations, but I can clearly differentiate the respect for the aesthetics that is present, in addition to a clearly and concisely visual identity, equipped with an eminently practical sense.\r\n\r\nThank you very much and really hope to see you in September.','2011-06-16 15:29:50','2011-06-16 15:29:50'),(51,17,'email_address','alvaro.bootello@gmail.com','2011-06-16 15:29:50','2011-06-16 15:29:50'),(52,18,'name','Remco Osorio Lobato ','2011-06-17 03:22:11','2011-06-17 03:22:11'),(53,18,'comments',' I Love the new site and program of theme\'s and speakers... and I hope to get à chance to take part, for at least one day, in this years event in Amsterdam...!','2011-06-17 03:22:11','2011-06-17 03:22:11'),(54,18,'email_address','Osoriolobato@gmail.com','2011-06-17 03:22:11','2011-06-17 03:22:11'),(55,19,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-06-17 09:14:49','2011-06-17 09:14:49'),(56,19,'comments','Bug ! .... profile shows 75 points , leaderboard shows 79 points ... competitive ? ... me ? .... never !','2011-06-17 09:14:49','2011-06-17 09:14:49'),(57,19,'email_address','barryslounge@googlemail.com','2011-06-17 09:14:49','2011-06-17 09:14:49'),(58,20,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-06-20 09:13:28','2011-06-20 09:13:28'),(59,20,'comments','Can you date stamp posts/discussions/comments to profile ? It would be helpful. Thanks .','2011-06-20 09:13:28','2011-06-20 09:13:28'),(60,20,'email_address','barryslounge@googlemail.com','2011-06-20 09:13:28','2011-06-20 09:13:28'),(61,21,'name','Remko','2011-06-28 21:16:41','2011-06-28 21:16:41'),(62,21,'comments','Hi!\r\n\r\nI have just tried to sign up with Facebook and was asked an email address. I didn\'t get any further than that as it kept coming back with the following message:\r\n\r\nAlmost there...\r\nHi , thanks for using Facebook to sign up!\r\nFacebook provided this email address, you can change it if you want:\r\n\r\nSo I changed it and changed it and changed it... nothing happened. \r\n\r\nWhat\'s next?\r\n\r\nLooking forward to your reply.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nRemko Spaan\r\n+ 31 6 20 40 48 51\r\nvisit our website: www.sequoiatees.com\r\nlike us on facebook.com/sequoiatees\r\nfollow us on twitter.com/sequoiatees','2011-06-28 21:16:41','2011-06-28 21:16:41'),(63,21,'email_address','remkospaan@versatel.nl','2011-06-28 21:16:41','2011-06-28 21:16:41'),(64,22,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-06-29 07:35:44','2011-06-29 07:35:44'),(65,22,'comments','Cannot seem to log in via FaceBook from my iPod Touch.','2011-06-29 07:35:44','2011-06-29 07:35:44'),(66,22,'email_address','BarrysLounge@googlemail.com','2011-06-29 07:35:44','2011-06-29 07:35:44'),(67,23,'name','Thieme Hennis','2011-06-29 10:53:29','2011-06-29 10:53:29'),(68,23,'comments','change of platform:\r\nhi there, I am a researcher at the TU Delft and focus on motivation and participation in online communities. I will do research at Mediamatic on their Anymeta platform, so I would like to turn the question around: what made you switch to another platform? If it has to do with money (etc.), I don\'t want to know, but if it has to do with capabilities of the platform, I am very interested. \r\n\r\nI will sign up for the new platform as well, it looks very nice. If I have suggestions, I will let you know.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nThieme Hennis\r\n','2011-06-29 10:53:29','2011-06-29 10:53:29'),(69,23,'email_address','t.a.hennis@tudelft.nl','2011-06-29 10:53:29','2011-06-29 10:53:29'),(70,24,'name','Alex Dodig','2011-07-14 07:56:05','2011-07-14 07:56:05'),(71,24,'comments','Hi, new site is nice.\r\nLooking from the usability point of view, JavaScript is to heavy and causing browser to slow down, or freeze. \r\nAlso the content text <p> is a bit on the small size with it\'s light grey letters. I think just one size bigger and bit darker.\r\nRegards,\r\nAlex','2011-07-14 07:56:05','2011-07-14 07:56:05'),(72,24,'email_address','info@alexxdesign.com','2011-07-14 07:56:05','2011-07-14 07:56:05'),(73,25,'name','@alyosha19','2011-07-14 15:29:12','2011-07-14 15:29:12'),(74,25,'comments','Hi Picnic,\r\nHaving a persistent reminder about the dates of the Festival in the scrolling carousel would be helpful. \r\nBest,\r\nAl','2011-07-14 15:29:12','2011-07-14 15:29:12'),(75,25,'email_address','al.cadena@yahoo.com','2011-07-14 15:29:12','2011-07-14 15:29:12'),(76,26,'name','Femke Hameetman','2011-07-18 21:17:56','2011-07-18 21:17:56'),(77,26,'comments','I tried to post something under new media (a text, link and photo) when I tried to post it was gone....what did I do wrong?','2011-07-18 21:17:56','2011-07-18 21:17:56'),(78,26,'email_address','femke@museumlab.nl','2011-07-18 21:17:56','2011-07-18 21:17:56'),(79,27,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-07-20 21:06:59','2011-07-20 21:06:59'),(80,27,'comments','Love the message function but it does not seem to work from my iPad .','2011-07-20 21:06:59','2011-07-20 21:06:59'),(81,27,'email_address','BarrysLounge@googlemail.com','2011-07-20 21:07:00','2011-07-20 21:07:00'),(82,28,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-07-30 10:18:43','2011-07-30 10:18:43'),(83,28,'comments','Please can you drop in a link to make it easier to navigate from the Club section to the program .','2011-07-30 10:18:43','2011-07-30 10:18:43'),(84,28,'email_address','BarrysLounge@GoogleMail.com','2011-07-30 10:18:43','2011-07-30 10:18:43'),(85,29,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-07-31 22:45:34','2011-07-31 22:45:34'),(86,29,'comments','Still cannot send a message with a sit on my blanket request from my iPad . Remember once people get to PICNIC they may only have an iPad with them !','2011-07-31 22:45:34','2011-07-31 22:45:34'),(87,29,'email_address','BarrysLounge@googlemail.com','2011-07-31 22:45:34','2011-07-31 22:45:34'),(88,30,'name','Paul Venet','2011-08-01 10:49:49','2011-08-01 10:49:49'),(89,30,'comments','Currently, I can\'t access my account. I submitted a request for assistance, \"forgotten password\". A response indicated that I should receive an mail. None came.\r\nHow do I get assistance with access problems?','2011-08-01 10:49:49','2011-08-01 10:49:49'),(90,30,'email_address','pvenet@gmail.com','2011-08-01 10:49:49','2011-08-01 10:49:49'),(91,31,'name','Sydney Levinson','2011-08-08 12:56:58','2011-08-08 12:56:58'),(92,31,'comments','re the Program section - cannot seem to find a way of printing personalised program or seeing what sessions other people are going to ( apart from on a session by session basis ) - is it just me ? ','2011-08-08 12:56:58','2011-08-08 12:56:58'),(93,31,'email_address','barryslounge@googlemail.com','2011-08-08 12:56:58','2011-08-08 12:56:58');
